{"tid":1231993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清算CCTVB","createTime":"2019-06-16T14:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:03:21.000Z","uid":107368,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a74cfcf49cfb1865fade6f4451d3cc2476b590","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:14:33.000Z","msg":"記協專業守則<br />\n1.     新聞工作者有責任維持最高的專業及操守標準。<br />\n<br />\n2.     新聞工作者無論何時均應維護媒介自由採集消息﹑發表評論和批評的原則，<strong>並應致力消除扭曲﹑壓制及審查的情況。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3.     新聞工作者應致力確保所傳播的消息做到公平和準確，並應避免把評論和猜測當作消息，以及避免因扭曲﹑偏選或錯誤引述而造成虛假。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>4.     新聞工作者應盡速糾正任何構成損害的不確報導，並確保更正和道歉得到應有的重視，而在事件有一定的重要性時，應讓受批評者有回應的權利。</strong><br />\n<br />\n5.     新聞工作者應以正直的手段取得消息﹑照片及插圖。只有在公眾利益凌駕一切的情況下，才可以使用其他手段，而新聞工作者有權基於個人良知反對使用該手段。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6.     新聞工作者即使基於公眾利益的考慮，亦不應侵擾他人的悲哀和不幸。</strong><br />\n<br />\n7.     新聞工作者應保護秘密消息的來源。<br />\n<br />\n8.     新聞工作者不應接受賄賂或利誘，以致影響其履行專業職責。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>9.     新聞工作者不應因為廣告或其他考慮而扭曲或壓制真相。</strong><br />\n<br />\n10.     新聞工作者不應為鼓勵種族﹑膚色﹑信仰或性別歧視之類材料的始作俑者。<br />\n<br />\n11.     新聞工作者不應利用從履行職責獲得的消息而在消息公佈前謀取私利。<br />\n<br />\n長遠計必須正視CCTVB日日係到亂鳩咁報 <br />\n罷睇 追住佢地部cam黎屌都無大作用<br />\n哩幾日間唔中都有幾單黑警棄暗投明<br />\n<strong>我地都應該比個機會班CCTVB記者+主播</strong><br />\n<br />\n撤回送中 雖然都要講 <br />\n但更重要係<strong>政府公開澄清612並非暴動 無條件釋放示威者</strong><br />\n<br />\n跟住就到CCTVB都要作同樣公開聲明 糾正之前所有報導 以正視聽<br />\n法律巴打 CCTVB日日屈我地暴動 如果政府澄清左 咁又算唔算誹謗<br />\n<br />\nFollow up action<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkja.org.hk/%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkja.org.hk%2F%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2588%25B6%2F&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=65ac45c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkja.org.hk/%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E6%A9%9F%E5%88%B6/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/complaints/lodge_a_complaint.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fcomplaints%2Flodge_a_complaint.html&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=cf075834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/complaints/lodge_a_complaint.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/images/doc/complaint_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fba_archives.ofca.gov.hk%2Fcn%2Fimages%2Fdoc%2Fcomplaint_Chi.pdf&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=60a07e35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ba_archives.ofca.gov.hk/cn/images/doc/complaint_Chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"dd90f7f9c3a9f5f5d9e4165016e78fe275144b5b","tid":1231993,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bc8d901b48fab79cdef76687ccbe6e2c45d28a","tid":1231993,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"記協, CCTVB邊會理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826bc7dc8173be4dc39ff2e56a0d571eabae7bc8","tid":1231993,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"229cd73ce23db232d8bcfab9218faf9b12d08095","tid":1231993,"uid":8821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c227dd25564a732a7a467e739f212b1a3cd0f1d8","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73bc8d901b48fab79cdef76687ccbe6e2c45d28a","tid":1231993,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"記協, CCTVB邊會理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"目標 要令到全行都公認做過CCTVB既新聞工作者都係垃圾！if 佢地唔正面回應"},{"pid":"62ebbd17a627596b505b68721fdc9579140948cd","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5492b55cac03e1b64f9eddcea70e995d92a18b8b","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n繼續做野 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=c760301c\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d45c8b182b10cc7695ac052e38c5e710dde2e82","tid":1231993,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"其實真係要cctvb付返多少代價，實在太多廢中廢老受佢地影響"},{"pid":"07bb193a17ea0ac6cf65e813fb00655aea2d0acd","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d45c8b182b10cc7695ac052e38c5e710dde2e82","tid":1231993,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"其實真係要cctvb付返多少代價，實在太多廢中廢老受佢地影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"衣家有200萬人都唔夠 要長遠救港<br />\n唔可以放棄廢老廢中<br />\n就算係mission impossible都唔可以放任CCTVB"},{"pid":"b2ce19291aea2ba798d467ff6499426abf2ab82f","tid":1231993,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"就好似Gladiator 個四隻老虎咁 下下比人拉住 簡人黎咬！"}]}